Introduction

LOVElution was an eighth member sub-unit of the girl group tripleS under MODHAUS. It was the group's fourth sub-unit, which was created through tripleS' Two Big WAVes Grand Gravity in April 2023.

During this Gravity, the fourteen known members were divided into two units, LOVElution and EVOLution, through voting, while S15 and S16, unknown at that time, were already placed in one of these units. The seven members voted in LOVElution were YuBin, SeoYeon, Kaede, DaHyun, SoHyun, HyeRin, and Nien, in that order. Xinyu was then revealed as the last unit member on July 2, 2023, when she was revealed to be S15.

They made their debut on August 17, 2023, with the mini album "ↀ (MUHAN)". The sub-unit promoted for four months and it is unknown if MODHAUS ever plans for them to make a comeback.
